Lingling.

579
00:37:55,540 --> 00:37:56,940
Are we leaving like this?

580
00:37:56,950 --> 00:37:57,950
Or what?

581
00:37:58,190 --> 00:38:01,050
Do you want an autograph or a photo?

582
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:03,120
Li Dongyuan did it?

583
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:05,420
Who else could it be?

584
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:07,520
He did it to take revenge on you

585
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:09,220
for Baijie.

586
00:38:10,700 --> 00:38:12,510
Anyway, it is quite difficult to deal with him.

587
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:14,630
