588
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:15,630
Leave it to him.

589
00:38:15,910 --> 00:38:16,910
Perfect.

590
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:18,860
You're right.

591
00:38:19,180 --> 00:38:20,910
He's quite arrogant.

592
00:38:23,090 --> 00:38:25,820
Did you leave the clue to him on purpose?

593
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:29,910
You really did that?

594
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:31,020
Why?

595
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:34,360
Li Dongyuan called me last night.

596
00:38:34,420 --> 00:38:35,420
So I told him

597
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,620
as compensation for him.

598
00:38:38,060 --> 00:38:41,270
Besides, I don't want to be a bad guy like Mou Kai.

599
00:38:43,700 --> 00:38:44,830
You're right.

600
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:46,660
But why should we come here so early?

601
00:38:46,660 --> 00:38:47,860
We didn't sleep well.

602
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:49,520
This long journey was costly.

603
00:38:50,310 --> 00:38:52,390
After all, he's a friend of Tan Zaozao.

604
00:38:52,390 --> 00:38:53,510
I have to respect her.

605
00:38:53,510 --> 00:38:55,570
But since he didn't choose Obsidian,

606
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:57,230
it has nothing to do with me.

607
00:38:58,110 --> 00:39:00,190
I have money for gasoline.

608
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:04,790
How did White Deer persuade Zhang Yiqing?

609
00:39:06,180 --> 00:39:07,580
Think about Li Dongyuan.

610
00:39:07,750 --> 00:39:09,750
Think about his skills to persuade.

611
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:12,900
It makes sense.
